<h2 id="scalable-configurable-pluggable-designs">Scalable, configurable, Pluggable Designs</h2>
<p>All the tools we use does not have dependencies on database, thus able to scale to terabytes or petabytes of data per day. Keep your data for as long as you want and tap into the full picture when you need it most — you never know which data you might need when the next attack strikes. Create knowledge bases without any other tools. 100% RESTFUL API means any integration can be done with ease</p>

<p>Ingest from anywhere, anytime
Ingest data from your cloud, network, endpoints, applications — any source you like, really. The data can come from many sources, including:</p>

